Package: cleanroom.sim
Title: Clean-Room Staged Analysis Framework for TMLE in Pharmacoepidemiology
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Andrew N.", "Mertens", role = c("aut", "cre"),
                  email = "amertens@example.com")
Description: Implements a clean-room (staged) workflow applying TMLE to an
    HCV-AKI pharmacoepidemiology case study. Includes a data-generating process,
    four-stage analysis pipeline with explicit checkpoints and decision logging,
    TMLE and comparator estimators, and a simulation study comparing estimator
    performance under realistic violations.
